{"tid":2218561,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"re0算唔算已經超越左刀劍成為輕小動畫一哥？","createTime":"2020-09-26T10:01:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-01T03:38:25.000Z","uid":87394,"like":84,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"9d33893f6cbfa5d018eb5a13b67f7d4f39baccbb","tid":2218561,"uid":87394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:01:45.000Z","msg":"自問對動畫既評價一向都相當嚴格<br />\n呢種穿越漫通常都會因為不停重複劇情而覺得煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但re0穿越得黎劇情又獲獲新鮮唔會同你拖泥帶水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再睇住主角冇乜才能一路崩潰一路成長又好有代入感<br />\n角色個性又夠獨特惹人鐘意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成套野都算係近年少有0死角既動畫<br />\n見依家通街個個都識雷母email真係抵佢成功<br />\n我已經決定含淚將我心目中既動畫一哥由刀劍改為re0<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4584160a2a4faa8474bc34fe3c7aed9f9e1de7cd","tid":2218561,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"f2ade271839a98ab4958e7468702426f138e31ff","tid":2218561,"uid":198822,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"物語好睇啲 不過睇人啦"},{"pid":"00d46067b61170bf2132873fd3dda4cca3732b80","tid":2218561,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4584160a2a4faa8474bc34fe3c7aed9f9e1de7cd","tid":2218561,"uid":191467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:06:06.000Z","msg":"g持"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:08:51.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇到奧托冒死救老友咸能jor<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人生有個咁既手足真係無憾了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3647827595fb4bb5b4e887a366f8987ce54d5fbf","tid":2218561,"uid":87394,"like":1,"dislike":26,"score":-25,"quote":{"pid":"f2ade271839a98ab4958e7468702426f138e31ff","tid":2218561,"uid":198822,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T10:08:16.000Z","msg":"物語好睇啲 不過睇人啦"},"citedBy":1